Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:19.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}时间不会停留
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:33.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}心愿被风吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:38.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}喉咙干涩沙哑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知前方有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你我就像一组平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坚强的你从不回头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们将永远不再相交
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs60}我颓然而立 城市在视野中模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs60}只有你曾存在的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs60}冲垮心灵的堤坝
