Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 那么好的孩子会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有人死了吗…
